7a0a&_nc_ohc=9ukXOEu_DpAQ7kNvgEpQyT9&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAlIA7Z9iFNpVVhMmubf5EeIWrbUjIUrri73Ow4mBNNWg&oe=67235C82"}, "display_name": "Rustfall: Recon", "keywords": ["multiplayer", "survival", "free", "robot", "shooter"], "long_description": "You've been sent on a one way mission down to an abandoned city with the expectation of death, but will you persevere? Survive 15 days, either with allies or just yourself, by looting and exploring until the extraction team arrive. With volatile storms that close in and out, and nightly attacks that are embedded throughout your recon mission, the odds are against you in every way possible. \n\nThis game is in FULL BETA and is published simply to test for bugs and gather feedback.", "short_description": "You've been sent on a one way mission down to an abandoned city with the expectation of death, but will you persevere? Survive 15 days, with storms and nightly attacks embedded throughout, by looting and exploring until the extraction team arrive."}]}, "developer_name": "eggdev", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://eggdevportfolio.wordpress.com/eggdevs-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "eggdev", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://eggdevportfolio.wordpress.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "644354873106712"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "951277430875009